title: The Underground Railroad - Choose Your Own Adventure 175.pdf
description:
This book takes place in the era of slavery, and is YOUR journey to help black persons escape slavery through the Underground Railroad.

This is scanned from a "Discarded" Grand Rapids Public Library book I bought off eBay.  The biggest reason I'm not posting a whole lot more of these CYOA books, is that a lot of my books are still in New Condition, even though they are 20 to even 30+ years old... and I want to keep them in mint condition; books that I have duplicates of I'll go ahead and break-up the spine of one of them, so it can fit in the scanner...

Enjoy!
